HEADWORD: Maidenly
<hw>Maid"en*ly</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Like a maid; suiting a maid;
maiden-like; gentle, modest, reserved.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Must you be blushing ? . . . ⟦br⟧
